{"tid":1127385,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 港鐵模型 DIY】達人自製 1：160 超像真香港列車","createTime":"2019-04-27T05:39:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T08:16:59.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"46f5d8ae5348e03b3ee4c29789b2dd14a8df415b","tid":1127385,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:39:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2335000/2336586/20190425_mtr_02_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2335000%2F2336586%2F20190425_mtr_02_600.jpg&h=ae6292f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鐵道模型玩意在港漸見普及，不過市售的鐵道模型都以歐、美、日系為主。如果想玩香港列車，愛本土化的朋友，其中一個方法，就是 DIY 自己動手造。今次介紹的兩位本地鐵道模型發燒友 Tommy 與 Dennis，皆擁有 DIY 香港列車作品經驗：Tommy 藉 3D 打印技術，3D 打印「千九公主」SP1950 馬鐵，及已退役的 KCR 蘋頭火車；Dennis 自製輕鐵之餘、更把 1979 年通車的 MTR 第一代香港地鐵「白頭列車」重現眼前；有燈、可通電在軌道上行駛、車廂內外細節超像真，直教香港列車迷瘋狂！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2336586/【港鐵模型%20DIY】第一代地鐵、千九公主、黃頭火車、輕鐵集合！達人自製%201：160%20超像真香港列車\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2336586%2F%E3%80%90%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B%2520DIY%E3%80%91%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E4%BB%A3%E5%9C%B0%E9%90%B5%E3%80%81%E5%8D%83%E4%B9%9D%E5%85%AC%E4%B8%BB%E3%80%81%E9%BB%83%E9%A0%AD%E7%81%AB%E8%BB%8A%E3%80%81%E8%BC%95%E9%90%B5%E9%9B%86%E5%90%88%EF%BC%81%E9%81%94%E4%BA%BA%E8%87%AA%E8%A3%BD%25201%EF%BC%9A160%2520%E8%B6%85%E5%83%8F%E7%9C%9F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%88%97%E8%BB%8A&d=wHiIeFeeqtLxwJ75m5qcs5FIS2qdHEMyYfCy%2BeARyBE%3D&h=6fbbbc2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2336586/【港鐵模型%20DIY】第一代地鐵、千九公主、黃頭火車、輕鐵集合！達人自製%201：160%20超像真香港列車</a>"},{"pid":"d248009edcaa7515a47a143c0b0f4a3cd4bfea3d","tid":1127385,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T05:40:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content